name: Moss Agate Cocktail Ring
description:
A completely unique. amazing. one of a kind, one in the entire world ring. A really special moss agate stone with natural crystal formations which take hundreds and thousands of years to form. They form as molten rock begins to cool with trapped gases inside. The gases cause gaps in the rock. As groundwater flows through these gaps for century after century, minerals crystallize on the rock forming a blanket of intense crystallization...

Pictures taken in direct sunlight (1) and natural light (2). The stone is always slightly changing in colour and sparkles!

Sterling Silver (925).

Ring can be re-sized to your hearts desire for no cost. Please allow up to 5 days before shipping.
